General Assembly Senate Joint
Resolution No. 17
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1485
Referred to Committee on Judiciary
Introduced by:
SEN. WINFIELD, 10th Dist.
REP. STAFSTROM, 129th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF THE HONORABLE
JOHN L. CARBONNEAU, JR. OF EAST LYME TO BE A STATE
REFEREE.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of the
2 Honorable Jon L. Carbonneau, Jr. of East Lyme to be a State Referee, to
3 serve a term of eight years from May 5, 2026, is approved and
4 confirmed, and he is appointed a State Referee for said term.
